column8:
Good Evening Mr. Vajdl,

My name is Omar Bayat, and I’m a Property Consultant at White & Co. Real Estate, one of Dubai’s leading British-owned brokerages.

I’m reaching out regarding your unit in 1. May I ask if it’s currently vacant and available for rent? I have a qualified client actively searching in the building and would appreciate the opportunity to present your unit if available.

Looking forward to your response. Thank you, and have a lovely day ahead.

Best regards,  
Omar Bayat  
White & Co. Real Estate
